summary: This is an email from an FBI Special Agent to the Airline Reporting Corporation, transmitting a federal grand jury subpoena for records related to a child exploitation/human trafficking investigation. The email requests expedited compliance by February 7, 2020, and asks the organization not to notify the subscriber due to the sensitive nature of the investigation.

keyFacts: A federal grand jury subpoena was issued to the Airline Reporting Corporation as part of a child exploitation/human trafficking investigation.
The subpoena had an expedited compliance deadline of February 7, 2020.
The FBI requested that the Airline Reporting Corporation not notify the subscriber of the subpoena due to the sensitive nature of the investigation.
The correspondence indicates an active investigation into child exploitation/human trafficking was ongoing as of January 2020.
The document reference EFTA00153632 is included, linking it to the broader Epstein case document set.
